{"slug":"sirkuler-23-727e-11205","reference":"Sirkuler_23_727E","gazette":"General Directorate of Customs","title":"Brand and model declaration has been made mandatory for specific goods during customs declaration registration","date":"27 Ağustos 2023","bodyHtml":"<p>For items such as gaming consoles, robot vacuums, electric scooters, projectors, speakers, and headphones, it is now mandatory to declare the brand and model number in the BİLGE system on the item description screen as of 14.08.2023. Registration procedures cannot proceed without providing the relevant information.</p><table class=\"MsoNormalTable\" border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"3\" cellpadding=\"0\" width=\"100%\">\r\n <tbody><tr>\r\n  <td>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><br><br></p><p><o></o></p>\r\n  <u1></u1><u1></u1><u1></u1><u1></u1><u1></u1><u1></u1><u1></u1><u1></u1><u1></u1><u1></u1><u1></u1><u1></u1><u1></u1><table class=\"MsoNormalTable\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" width=\"368\">\r\n   <tbody><tr>\r\n    <td width=\"237\" valign=\"top\">\r\n    <br>\r\n    </td>\r\n    \r\n    <td width=\"131\" valign=\"top\">\r\n    <span>HS CODE</span></td>\r\n   </tr>\r\n   \r\n   <tr>\r\n    <td width=\"237\" valign=\"top\">\r\n    <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span>Game Consoles</span><o></o></p>\r\n    </td>\r\n    \r\n    <td width=\"131\" valign=\"top\">\r\n    <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span>9504.50.00.00.00</span><o></o></p>\r\n    </td>\r\n   </tr>\r\n   \r\n   <tr>\r\n    <td width=\"237\" valign=\"top\">\r\n    <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span>Robot vacuums ( Vacuum cleaners)</span><o></o></p>\r\n    </td>\r\n    \r\n    <td width=\"131\" valign=\"top\">\r\n    <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span>8508.11.00.00.11<u1></u1></span><o></o></p>\r\n    <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span>8508.11.00.00.19<u1></u1></span><o></o></p>\r\n    <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span>8508.19.00.00.00<u1></u1></span><o></o></p>\r\n    <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span>8509.80.00.00.19<u1></u1></span><o></o></p>\r\n    </td>\r\n   </tr>\